Blade Template
doc: https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/blade#introduction

1. What? 
https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/blade#introduction

    - Template engine
    - Its own loops, conditional statements
    - crete view file using .blade.php extension not ".php"
    
2. Displaying data
https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/blade#displaying-data

    - php:

    <?php
        echo $name;
    ?>
    - laravel blade: 
        1. {{}} - doesn't decode html print as it is
        2. {!! <h2> Name: </h2>!!} - ecode html and executes it

3. Blade directives
https://laravel.com/docs/9.x/blade#blade-directives

    - @if, @elseif, @end @endif
    - @unless @endunless
    - @isset @endisset
    - @for
    - @while 
    - @foreach
    - @break & continue
4. Creating layouts in blade Template
    - @yield
    - @secion
    - @extends
    